. 
<emphasis id="B955751CFF84D93FBFF32D7EFE5B8729" bold="true" box="[472,489,1805,1826]" pageId="4" pageNumber="125">A</emphasis>
. Flowering branch. 
<emphasis id="B955751CFF84D93FBC822D7EFD0B8729" bold="true" box="[681,697,1805,1826]" pageId="4" pageNumber="125">B</emphasis>
. Inflorescence detail. 
<emphasis id="B955751CFF84D93FBDA12D7EFC298728" bold="true" box="[906,923,1805,1827]" pageId="4" pageNumber="125">C</emphasis>
. Flower at anthesis. 
<emphasis id="B955751CFF84D93FBA742D7EFBC28729" bold="true" box="[1119,1136,1805,1826]" pageId="4" pageNumber="125">D</emphasis>
. Antepetalous stamen, side view. 
<emphasis id="B955751CFF84D93FBEA32D42FF2A874D" bold="true" box="[136,152,1841,1862]" pageId="4" pageNumber="125">E</emphasis>
. Antesepalous stamen in side (L) and ventral view (R) (
<emphasis id="B955751CFF84D93FBC992D42FC8A874D" box="[690,824,1841,1862]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="125">Cardenas 823</emphasis>
, NY).
</paragraph>
